# Sales Prospecting Workspace Skill Profile

This file defines the default behavior for an SDR/prospecting workspace.

## Intended behavior

- Fast first response: brief, actionable, and oriented around next steps.
- Ask at most one clarifying question when the user goal is unclear.
- Trigger background hydration so follow-up questions (competitors, customers,
  product) become cheaper and faster.

